---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Me">
  <section class="about">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>
      I’m a third-year MEng Mathematical Computation student at University College London, currently exploring machine learning and software engineering.
    </p>

    <div class="resume-section">
      <h3>Resume</h3>
      <p>
        You can download full resume here:
        <a href="/resume.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="default-link">Resume (PDF)</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="recommendation-section">
      <h3>Letters</h3>

      <p>
        A short recommendation letter from Prof. Tobias Ritschel, after we had a chat about some variance reduction tricks for Monte Carlo integration in path tracing.
        <a href="/letter/Ritschel_letter.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="default-link">Letter (PDF)</a>
        <span class="letter-date">(11 Mar 2025)</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        A short recommendation from Prof. Earl T. Barr, after I got the top score in COMP0010 Software Engineering. It was used to support my funding application for a 2023–24 summer project.
        <a href="/letter/Earl_letter.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="default-link">Letter (PDF)</a>
        <span class="letter-date">(15 March 2024)</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .about {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .resume-section {
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .recommendation-section {
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .letter-date {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #888;
      margin-left: 0.5rem;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
